title: Jenkins and Jonez - Steve A. Smith and Russell Westbrook Have Some Thinking To Do
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - Steve A. Smith and Russell Westbrook Have Some Thinking To Do
description:
The guys discuss 110 episodes of Joe Rogan’s podcast being taken off Spotify, Steve A. Smith and Kevin Durant’s latest beef, Russell Westbrook being booed by Lakers fans, Ja Morant making the Grizzlies the most fun team in the league, how to steal a gold cube from Central Park, and much more. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
